OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine
OL,6,Finitially, but becoming rather cloudy
OL,7,Ffrom the west, with outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fspreading eastwards throughout the
OL,9,Fnight, perhaps seen more widely
OL,10,Ftowards dawn. Staying warm and muggy
OL,11,Fwith light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FBrightest in the southeast,
OL,14,Fwith the greatest chance of some sunny
OL,15,Fspells here. Cloudier elsewhere, with
OL,16,Fperiods of mostly light rain, easing
OL,17,Flater. Generally warm and rather humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
